{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it compulsory for schools to first aid train all staff",
        "additional_details": "A non-first-aid trained teacher might be alone in a classroom full of children. If a child was to need first aid, the teacher would have to seek a first-aid trained teacher to administer first aid. This would take time and could mean a child doesn't receive first aid until it is too late.",
        "background": "This could save lives in emergency situations, when immediate action is needed. If all staff are first aid trained, it should reduce time spent trying to find a first aider.",
